// install packages
general: npm i (package_name)

example:    npm i express --save
'--save'      --> not required

'node_modules' ---> it contains all the packages installed
package-lock.json       --> contains the details about all sub-dependencies
update: package.json ---> dependencies updated



use: npm i  ---> to redownload the 'node_modules' folder with package.json and package-lock.json


// install globally
npm i -g nodemon                ---> refreshes the http

// install only for development
npm install --save-dev nodemon


// uninstall packages

npm unistall express


